iKraal | Jelena for Tesco (UK)

Jelena for Tesco (UK)

Jelena from iKraal on Vimeo.

Jelena for Tesco (UK) – We spent a week shooting summer fashion inserts for London based chain store Tesco. Making the most of the Cape Town summer to shoot their still catalogue for the up and coming queens jubilee we where asked to cover the story for a behind the scenes video for the Tesco magazine website.

While we were at it we shot some general fashion videos with a few of the models which is always a bit of fun.

All shot on Canon 5D MarkII.

All about White Romwe Minimal Shirts

White Romwe Minimal Shirts first appeared on Chictopia's streetstyle gallery in Summer 2014 seen on KATOWICE blogger asymetria of iamsony.blogspot.com. She styled her white romwe minimal shirt with a carrot orange 6ks floral skirt. Since then, White Romwe Minimal Shirts have grown in popularity as bloggers from KATOWICE have discovered them. White Romwe Minimal Shirts are generally seen in romantic style. Popular types of White Romwe Shirts are leopard print, lace, chiffon, floral, and polka dot.
